dreisoft.tresos.tresosdb.api.model.v2.commonstructure.serviceneeds

Interface IDiagnosticIoControlNeeds

  • All Superinterfaces:
    IDiagnosticCapabilityElement, IEntity, IIdentifiable, IReferrable, IServiceNeeds

    public interface IDiagnosticIoControlNeeds
extends IEntity, IDiagnosticCapabilityElement
    IDiagnosticIoControlNeeds: Entity class of the tresosDB model.

    Specifies the general needs on the configuration of the Diagnostic Communication Manager (DCM) which are not related to a particular item (e.g. a PID). The main use case is the mapping of service ports to the Dcm which are not related to a particular item.
